input.value:
fetch logs
| filter k8s.namespace.name=="tracee"
| parse log, "JSON:json_log"
| fieldsAdd processname=json_log[processName], hostname=json_log[hostName],eventname=json_log[eventName],policicies=json_log[matchedPolicies] , k8s_json=json_log[kubernetes], contain_json=json_log[container], syscall=json_log[syscall]
| fieldsAdd containername=contain_json[name], pod_name=k8s_json[podName], pod_namespace=k8s_json[podNamespace], policy_0=policicies[0]
| fieldsRemove contain_json, k8s_json, policicies


| summarize count() , by:{eventname}

fetch logs
| filter k8s.namespace.name=="tracee"
| parse log, "JSON:json_log"
| fieldsAdd processname=json_log[processName], hostname=json_log[hostName],eventname=json_log[eventName],policicies=json_log[matchedPolicies] , k8s_json=json_log[kubernetes], contain_json=json_log[container], syscall=json_log[syscall]
| fieldsAdd containername=contain_json[name], pod_name=k8s_json[podName], pod_namespace=k8s_json[podNamespace], policy_0=policicies[0]
| fieldsRemove contain_json, k8s_json, policicies
| filter policy_0 == "otel-http-traffic"
| fieldsAdd args=json_log[args]
| fieldsadd metadata=args[0], detail=args[1]
| fieldsAdd valuevalue=detail[value]
| fieldsRemove detail

| filter eventname == "net_packet_http_request"
| fieldsAdd httpmethod=valuevalue[method], host=valuevalue[host], uri=valuevalue[uri_path]
| fieldsRemove valuevalue
| summarize count(), by:{ bin(timestamp, 60s),pod_name, uri,httpmethod}
